      "rationale": "Blood analog properties taken from published rheological data with ±3% uncertainty on dynamic viscosity. Inlet velocity profiles derived from Doppler ultrasound measurements. Rotational speed uncertainty ±0.5%. Input uncertainty bounds propagated through Monte Carlo sampling (500 runs) to characterize output distribution on NIH. Note: we plan to extend this UQ effort with a formal sensitivity analysis to rank the dominant input drivers by their contribution to NIH variance, but this ranking has not yet been completed for the current submission."
