    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with Medium model influence. Uncertainty quantification via Monte Carlo propagation confirms NIH output distribution satisfies RH < 1 at the 95th percentile across all 5 operating conditions. The package is accepted for regulatory submission supporting worst-case hemolysis identification for the CPB device.",
